ng-thu-v%C3%B4-nguy%E1%BB%87t-tam-nh%E1%BA%ADt-h%E1%BA%ADu-h%E1%BB%91t-nhi%C3%AAn-t%C3%ACnh-c%E1%BA%A3m-t%C3%A1c/poem-JgdVZfO32jc_MouEhtHb5g">Trung thu vô nguyệt, tam nhật hậu hốt nhiên tình, cảm tác - 中秋無月三日後忽然晴感作</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-T%C3%BAc/T%C3%B9ng-qu%E1%BB%91c-c%C3%B4ng-l%E1%BA%A1p-mai-%E1%BB%A9ng-gi%C3%A1o/poem-uqmyjS9jm6xZSY6Thu0eaQ">Tùng quốc công lạp mai ứng giáo - 從國公臘梅應教</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-T%C3%BAc/author-DYGad0thHvgCxK3Szp1zVQ">Trần Đình Túc</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Qu%C3%BD-%C4%90%C3%B4n/V%E1%BB%8Dng-Thanh-Hoa-nh%E1%BA%A5t-%C4%91%E1%BB%9Bi-duy%C3%AAn-s%C6%A1n-ng%E1%BA%ABu-th%C3%A0nh/poem-2X6f1k8pu8NqOC0U9oXJ_Q">Vọng Thanh Hoa nhất đới duyên sơn ngẫu thành - 望清華一帶緣山偶成</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Qu%C3%BD-%C4%90%C3%B4n/author-YDc3orDW4enWycHMfed3Ww">Lê Quý Đôn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-H%E1%BB%97/Xa-dao-dao/poem-Ashbl76IM1u_LcF1E04I_g">Xa dao dao - 車遙遙</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-H%E1%BB%97/author-uSefdg6gWPnl7XHeM-UXCw">Trương Hỗ</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
